com.i2group.apollo.events.transport

Interface IChangeSet<TChange extends IIdentifiable,TNew extends IIdentifiable>

  • Type Parameters:
    TChange - The type that describes the changes to existing data.
    TNew - The type that added new data. This is typically the type of data that is the subject of the TChange changes.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IItemChangeSet, IItemChangeSetCommand
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddCardToItem, AmendCardOnItem, CardAddedToItemEvent, CardAmendedEvent, CardDeletedFromItemEvent, CreateEntity, CreateLink, DeleteCardFromItem, EntityCreatedEvent, EntityMergedEvent, LinkCreatedEvent, PropertyChangeSet, PropertyGroupChangeSet

    public interface IChangeSet<TChange extends IIdentifiable,TNew extends IIdentifiable>
    A set of changes made to an object in the Analysis Repository by executing a command.
    Since:
    1.0
